#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/materials/special_effects/halo.rst:192
msgid ""
"Add a material for the billboard, and set it to the type *Halo*. Set the "
"*Halo Size* to 0.06 and when you render the scene you should see a grid "
"of white spots."
