"render. You should now have only red dots, but the billboard is still too"
" dark. To fix this enter *Edit Mode* for the board and copy all vertices "
"using the :kbd:`Shift-D` shortcut (take care not to move them!). Then "
"adjust the brightness with the *Add* value in the Halo panel."
